window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In Catherine Aird’s <i>Stiff News</i>, a letter received by an old woman’s son after her death alerts Detective Inspector C. D. Sloan that one woman’s death by natural causes in a local nursing home may actually be murder. But that is just the beginning of the odd goings-on in this nursing home catering to former members of a WWII regiment.</p>"; 
